data.text:
Dude, Where's My Napkin?

Katie and Greg enjoy a night on the town with Angela's ex after Celeste, an editor, helps Greg land his first book deal. But Angela, who has asked Katie not to socialize with her former wife, is furious and accuses her of being a bad friend.

What Goes Around Came Around

Bent on revenge, Bud makes a date with the girl who once stole his clothes and ran his underwear up the flagpole.

The Penultimate / Ode To Joy

[Season Finale] David expresses his feelings for Donna by writing her a giant love note in the sand. Dylan graduates from California University. Matt considers moving to New York to help his sister-in-law raise her child.

Maya Judging Amy

Maya hires a smart new assistant who doesn't hesitate to use her beauty as an asset at work.
